This paper deals with text classification using word embeddings and LSTM neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves social media analysis, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves information retrieval, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves political classification, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
